law.catch_line: Medicaid managed care organization to comply with KRS 304.17A-740 to 304.17A-743.
law.text: A managed care organization that provides Medicaid benefits pursuant to this chapter shall comply with the provisions of KRS 304.17A-740 to 304.17A-743.
law.history: Created 2012 Ky. Acts ch. 20, sec. 3, effective July 12, 2012.
